的虚构人物，但纯游戏或影视剧原创人物暂不可选。 足球队至少为 11 人，篮球队至少为 5 人，排球队至少为 6 人，你可根据需要增加替补球员，球员性别无任何限制。 成功组队者可获知乎宇宙赞助的 2022 年任意一场三大球赛事的入场券一张。 以上就是本次活动的全部内容，最后老西祝球迷朋友们观战愉快，非球迷朋友也要注意运动和锻炼，愿每一位来小沙龙做客的朋友都永葆健康和活力！ 更多精彩敬请移步：西斯特艾伦：西公公的活动场沙龙集锦——三国人物主题派对（长期更新）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picb.zhimg.com/50/v2-7b175f148341274dc0e7e504167a4416_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "47 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/471430074"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IkNuyx/2csKR+EAMaCDY3MDQxNzAxII6ypocGMAA4O0Amcgk0NzE0MzAwNzR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1626275495.478955", "card_id": "Q_287989193", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 76}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "七夕节送男朋友什么礼物好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "本人大学生，价格不要太高，手表他有，腰带、手串、火机、娃娃都送过，他一般去网吧所以鼠标键盘除外"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-169f4d859147fefa1e848ab72a5cde95_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "45 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/287989193"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IkNuyx/2csKR+EAMaCDI2Mjc0NDQ2IJOOh9sFMAI4gQJAJ3IJMjg3OTg5MTkzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "40_1626275495.479446", "card_id": "Q_346057428", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 751}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "买机械键盘是交智商税吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-183236824f8724bc89f6bf0fd030cc4c_720w.jpg?source=2044ae36"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "44 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/346057428"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IkNuyx/2csKR+EAMaCDM5MTc5MTc2IKrq9esFMD44kQtAKHIJMzQ2MDU3NDI4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "41_16262